        " «إِذَا قَضَى مَنَاسِكَ اَلْحَجِّ فَلْيَصْنَعْ مَا شَاءَ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2830 - It is narrated that Yahya al-Azraq asked Abu Abdullah (as):\n\"Is it permissible for a person to perform Tawaf on behalf of his relatives?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"If he has completed the rites of Hajj, then he may do as he wishes.\""
        ]
